data.description: No Specials with this 5-bedroom, 3-bath, 3-car garage, large corner cul-de-sac lot in beautiful Cedar Park subdivision and Andover School District. The foyer opens to the vaulted-ceiling living room with gas fireplace with decorative tile surround. Several windows provide a nice view of the tree-filled back yard and open view to the neighborhood park across the street. The large kitchen with eating bar, granite countertops, and pull out shelves as well as the dining room have beautiful wood floors. Main floor laundry and hall pantry. The coffered ceiling Master suite is on the main level with a walk-in closet. The master bath has two sinks, large tub, and a separate shower. The view out basement features a 35-foot family room with a dry bar, 2 bedrooms, a full bath, and storage. Entertain on the east-facing deck or the huge concrete patio and relax while you enjoy the convenience of the sprinkler system and irrigation well. The garage has loft storage, with the two-car garage on one side, and the third garage closes off from the other and can be utilized as a shop. New roof and gutters 4 years ago. The neighborhood playground and ponds are close, and Red Bud Walking Trail is nearby, too! Schedule your showing today!
